  "detailed_description": "<h1>UPDATE HISTORY</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/fbcb5ff407ed5c5c28490ffb2a00aa0f.avif?t=1773940330\" width=616 height=1836 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/b0faeefc7a21e2457a90c43527d203d2.avif?t=1773940330\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DISCOVER YOUR PATH</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture into a lawless frontier where survival depends on every decision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each biome - from burning deserts to haunted swamps and frozen peaks - presents unique threats and rare opportunities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sub-biomes, hidden routes, and unpredictable enemies keep every run fresh.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you outlast the wild? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/d370eb3e68b19fc625817c1f469647d5.poster.avif?t=1773940330\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/d370eb3e68b19fc625817c1f469647d5.webm?t=1773940330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/d370eb3e68b19fc625817c1f469647d5.mp4?t=1773940330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BRING YOUR BASE CAMP WITH YOU</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don’t find safety - you build it.<br>Grow and customize your mobile Base Camp to follow you through the frontier.<br>Upgrade workbenches, secure resources, and expand your shelter as you push deeper into the wild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world that never stops hunting you, your camp is your only constant. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/66f7b55f7a54d9f3aa812685a450c345.poster.avif?t=1773940330\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/66f7b55f7a54d9f3aa812685a450c345.webm?t=1773940330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/66f7b55f7a54d9f3aa812685a450c345.mp4?t=1773940330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MASTER THE ART OF GUN FIGHT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Face ambushes, predators, and bounty hunters in high-stakes ranged combat.<br>Use rifles, throwables, and quick instincts to survive escalating firefights.<br>As your bounty rises, enemies grow tougher and more aggressive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you thrive under pressure - or fall to the hunt? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/121eac7f28ab38a5fe9ad2f25cc05c27.poster.avif?t=1773940330\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/121eac7f28ab38a5fe9ad2f25cc05c27.webm?t=1773940330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/121eac7f28ab38a5fe9ad2f25cc05c27.mp4?t=1773940330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HANDCRAFT YOUR TOOLKIT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay alive by scavenging, crafting, and planning ahead. Manage hunger, thirst, temperature, and health as you move through deadly terrain. Every resource counts. Every mistake costs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt, improvise - or die.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/d0b80def9e8d56fbee3132316d01f6a6.poster.avif?t=1773940330\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/d0b80def9e8d56fbee3132316d01f6a6.webm?t=1773940330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2481670/extras/d0b80def9e8d56fbee3132316d01f6a6.mp4?t=1773940330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you prepared to survive?</strong></p>",
